1
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:43,370
Fujiko-san, you need to be careful. There are icy patches on this path.

2
00:01:43,700 --> 00:01:45,500
R-Right!

3
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:52,130
I-Ino... Ino... Inokuma-san?

4
00:01:52,130 --> 00:01:55,510
How many laps are you going to run along this bank?

5
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:57,380
Ten laps.

6
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,800
That sounds grueling!

7
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:03,350
But you need to get back into shape, so let's go for it.

8
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:06,140
Come on, let's run, Fujiko-san!

9
00:02:06,140 --> 00:02:07,480
Okay!

10
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,100
Inokuma-san...

11
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:14,520
Fujiko-san...

12
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:19,320
I'm sorry for making you worry for so long.

13
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:22,830
Do not take Inokuma Yawara lightly!

14
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:29,710
She's a prodigy. She's not affected by an absence, you hear me?

15
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:35,090
That prodigy has now gotten serious. I've seen it with my own two eyes!

16
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:39,310
And it gave me goose bumps!

17
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,380
Kazamatsuri-kun.

18
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:47,060
Y-Yes, sir?

19
00:02:48,390 --> 00:02:50,600
We're retraining her from the beginning!

20
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:53,270
Make sure all journalists are shut out.

21
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:54,940
We're on lockdown!

22
00:02:55,820 --> 00:03:02,820
The Explosive Remark!



23
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:12,830
What should we do, Matsuda-san? We'll never get an article.

24
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:16,800
So that celebutante Honami Sayaka has locked out reporters? </i>

25
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:20,980
What kind of secret training is she conducting behind those doors?</i>

26
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,430
K-Kaga-kun?

27
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,760
Huh?

28
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:26,930
Kosaku!

29
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:33,310
H-How did you get inside, Kuniko-san?




30
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:37,320
Oh, that security guard was almost too easy!

31
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:42,570
S-So were you able to see Honami Sayaka's secret training taking place inside?

32
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:44,570
I saw it, all right.

33
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:49,330
All right! We've got a huge scoop!

34
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:53,290
No way, it's not even worth an article!

35
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:59,340
Sayaka-san was just having sex with Kazamatsuri-san!



36
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,340
It got so ridiculous that I left!

37
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:02,840
I swear to gosh!

38
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:06,800
H-Having sex with Kazamatsuri?

39
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:23,640
I-I think we've done enough, Sayaka-san.

40
00:04:27,450 --> 00:04:29,870
No, we're not through yet!

41
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:45,090
Are you all right, Fujiko-san? Let's call it a day.

42
00:04:46,390 --> 00:04:50,280
I'm fine. Honestly, I'm A-OK.

43
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:53,350
Besides, I need to give Fuku-chan her milk.

44
00:04:53,350 --> 00:04:55,970
That's all right. I'll do it!

45
00:04:55,970 --> 00:04:59,860
You should take a shower and get a massage from Grandpa!

46
00:05:00,190 --> 00:05:05,240
N-No way! I let you take care of everything for me!

47
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,330
I'm fine...


48
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,370
Fujiko-san!

49
00:05:10,370 --> 00:05:13,370
Headline: The All-Japan Championship Draws Near!
Near: Another Struggle Between Honami, Inokuma, and Ito?
Far sidebar: Clash of the Three Titans Approaches!!#

50
00:05:13,370 --> 00:05:18,380
Things are getting hot! Only a few more days till the All-Japan!

51
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:20,400
Are you listening, Grandpa?

52
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:22,380
What is it? Time to eat?


53
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:24,360
I didn't say that!

54
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:27,180
I'm saying Fujiko-san can't compete in the All-Japan Championships!

55
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,800
Whaddaya mean, she can't?

56
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:31,180
She can do anything she puts her mind to!

57
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:35,440
You should know since you've been giving her massages!

58
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,840
She's really exhausted!



59
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,690
She's been absent for a long time.

60
00:05:38,690 --> 00:05:41,240
And don't forget she just gave birth!

61
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,190
She also has her hands full raising a child!

62
00:05:44,660 --> 00:05:46,940
I know darn well she's having a hard time!

63
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:52,290
I know 'cause as a young'un, I spent three days and three nights up on that mountain facing bears—

64
00:05:52,290 --> 00:05:55,590
Grandpa, that wasn't normal. Don't compare it with her!

65
00:05:55,590 --> 00:05:57,790
That's right. I'm a wunderkind!



66
00:05:57,790 --> 00:06:00,040
I'll make it through the tournament.

67
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:05,840
Just keep Fujiko-san out of the All-Japan and have her focus on the All-Japan Selected!

68
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:08,220
What if she gets injured because she wasn't ready?

69
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,610
You dummy!

70
00:06:09,610 --> 00:06:15,680
You and Beanpole will sweep every tournament I enter you guys in with flying colors!

71
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,180
Grandpa!

72
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:20,190
Quit yapping and get my food, dangit!

73
00:06:22,690 --> 00:06:24,690
Sign: Oshiuri TV#

74
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:27,610
Please, Master Inokuma, right this way.

75
00:06:27,610 --> 00:06:29,340
We've called a taxi for you.



76
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:32,330
Thanks. We going somewhere to eat?

77
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:37,080
My word, that was a magnificent answer to a life problem, Master!

78
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:40,710
A wife's relationship with her mother-in-law can't be built in a day!

79
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,750
Sign: Straight Answers to Life's Problems#

80
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:45,620
Ah, I couldn't put it any better myself!



81
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:51,090
My daily training is a gift that keeps on giving!

82
00:06:51,090 --> 00:06:55,440
Hey, that's Grandpa Inokuma. He's been on TV a lot lately!

83
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,880
Wait, isn't this a bad time?

84
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,700
Why?

85
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:02,500
Honami Sayaka's on our program today!

86
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:05,070
You know those two are like oil and water!



87
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:11,560
We thank you for your wonderful comment on fashion!

88
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,950
Crap! Speak of the devil!

89
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:15,830
Oh no!


90
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:19,500
As you know, beauty comes from within.

91
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:22,660
I will still exude beauty even if you leave me in my natural state.

92
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:23,330
Of course.


93
00:07:23,330 --> 00:07:25,500
Life is a never-ending training session.

94
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:28,710
If you don't train as hard as me— Huh?

95
00:07:29,590 --> 00:07:33,590
Plain people can talk about training and tempering themselves.

96
00:07:33,590 --> 00:07:37,640
I, however, have shone ever since the day I was born.

97
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,560
Well, well.



98
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:46,070
It has been ages.

99
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:49,940
What? Grandpa Inokuma and Miss Sayaka ran into each other?

100
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:50,490
All right!

101
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,030
This is gold!


102
00:07:52,030 --> 00:07:55,490
This is no time to be chasing after the Miyazawa Rika scandal!

103
00:07:55,490 --> 00:08:00,710
You sure you wanna be traipsing around here in the middle of your "secret training"?

104
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:04,200
There's nothing actually secret about it.

105
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:09,760
If I receive too much attention, it will eclipse Yawara-san's big comeback.

106
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:15,220
The media attention her comeback is receiving will prove short-lived,

107
00:08:15,670 --> 00:08:19,120
as I will soon beat her back into oblivion.

108
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:23,230
I am generously letting her live out her dream before time runs out.

109
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:29,730
Then I guess you're entering the All-Japan Championships, ain't ya?

110
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,240
Of course I am!






111
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:37,990
What is it? What is so funny?

112
00:08:38,490 --> 00:08:42,750
We're withdrawing from the All-Japan!

113
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:45,250
Wh-What did you say?

114
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:52,050
You didn't have to take such a coward's way out!

115
00:08:52,050 --> 00:08:54,540
Are you that afraid of me?

116
00:08:57,430 --> 00:08:58,780
Don't be stupid!

117
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:01,140
I'm just givin' you the spotlight.

118
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:03,980
Y-You are giving me... the spotlight?

119
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,690
That's right!

120
00:09:05,690 --> 00:09:12,140
You can enter the All-Japan, win the ribbon, and have the glory all to yourself.

121
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:15,360
You get to sit on the queen's throne a wee bit longer.




122
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,900
We're good with just one tournament.

123
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:22,370
With just the All-Japan Selected.

124
00:09:22,370 --> 00:09:27,370
We'll win the ticket to Barcelona with just that one contest!

125
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:32,880
Till then, I hope that throne feels good under your butt!

126
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,360
Let's go!



127
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:37,220
Come on!

128
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:40,540
Grandpa...

129
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:45,600
He thought about what's good for Fujiko-san.

130
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:49,300
He could have been a lot more honest, though.

131
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:53,860
The nerve of him!

132
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:57,110
In that case, I won't enter the All-Japan either!

133
00:09:57,110 --> 00:10:00,080
I-Is that so? Then I agree!



134
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:03,200
I am worn out from all that rigorous training anyway.

135
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,200
No.

136
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,580
You're entering.

137
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:08,620
Don't let that old man get to you.

138
00:10:08,620 --> 00:10:11,960
You still need each and every one of those live matches as practice!

139
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:22,730
Sign: National Martial Arts Hall#

140
00:10:26,580 --> 00:10:27,480
Ippon!


141
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:29,940
She's strong, overwhelmingly strong!

142
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:33,940
Honami makes it to the finals easily!

143
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:36,740
She's really proven how powerful she is!

144
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:38,280
What do you think, Saito-san?

145
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:42,450
Ah, "brilliant" is the only word I can use to describe her today!


146
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:46,400
She's definitely confident after sweeping every major tournament last year,

147
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:50,960
but she's winning here with moves that are speedier and smoother than ever before!



148
00:10:51,330 --> 00:10:56,630
Her secret training away from the media must be behind that.

149
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,720
Indeed!

150
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,470
Wrong!


151
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:02,470
W-Wrong?

152
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:05,380
That was a comment from our special guest, Master Inokuma Jigoro.

153
00:11:05,380 --> 00:11:06,560
What do you mean by that?

154
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:09,900
She's still that highfalutin' heiress!

155
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:12,380
If you can get that good through mere practice,

156
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:16,800
she'd have opened that practice to the public, however much of an eyesore it was.

157
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,940
Right, Saito?

158
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:19,460
Oh? Yes.




159
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:24,450
So you're saying Honami has some sort of secret weapon?

160
00:11:24,450 --> 00:11:26,060
Of course she does!

161
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:31,220
She's got a trick up her sleeve that she'll use in the upcoming Selected against Yawara!

162
00:11:31,220 --> 00:11:33,210
She ain't gonna give us no preview of it!

163
00:11:33,210 --> 00:11:35,590
Well, she'll whip it out sooner or later.

164
00:11:35,590 --> 00:11:38,710
We'll just sit back, eat some snacks, and watch for it!




165
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:41,880
Here, eat up, Saito. You too, announcer guy!

166
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,470
Nah!

167
00:11:42,470 --> 00:11:46,320
Oh, God! Grandpa, you're embarrassing me!

168
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:48,680
But Sayaka-san is really strong!

169
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:53,140
What? When it comes to Inokuma, Honami is just a fart in the wind.

170
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:54,400
Right, Fuku-chan?

171
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:57,980
Don't teach her those words!

172
00:11:57,980 --> 00:12:01,070
Anyway, Master Jigoro is right.

173
00:12:01,070 --> 00:12:06,240
It all comes down to what sort of secret training your dad is giving Sayaka-san.

174
00:12:07,490 --> 00:12:08,660
Dad...

175
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:17,250
Wow! There goes a favorite to win this tournament, Tohdoh Yuki!

176
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,420
Ippon!

177
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:22,360
Tohdoh is finished!

178
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:25,420
It's Takabe! Tababe with a marvelous Sasae Tsurikomi Ashi!

179
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:29,470
It was a fight between two strong veterans, and Takabe's strategy came out on top!

180
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:33,840
Compared to the flamboyant Honami,
 Takabe Yoko hasn't gotten much notice.

181
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,280
But she's definitely a skilled player!






182
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:39,190
She won her matches with a subtle,
 refined grace, and now she's in the finals!

183
00:12:39,190 --> 00:12:43,860
These two polar opposites will battle for the throne!

